        "title": "Summary",
        "category": "summary",
        "text": "The latest version of SIMATIC NET PC-Software fixes a vulnerability that could allow remote\nattackers to cause a Denial-Of-Service on several OPC-UA ports under certain conditions.\nAFFECTED PRODUCTS\nSIMATIC NET PC-Software: All versions < V13 SP2\nDESCRIPTION\nSIMATIC NET PC-Software is required for communication between controllers (PLCs) and\nPC based solutions (HMIs).\nDetailed information about the vulnerability is provided below."
